      "text": "We're hiring.  We ask candidates to write some code before we talk to them.  Which means we have to run other people's code on our laptops.  Natural incentives should discourage a job hunter from attacking a potential employer.  But I don't trust incentives.  So I've taken to running their code in docker.  You can too."
