      "text": "cd ~/Downloads/candidates-code\n\ndocker pull openjdk:8-alpine\ndocker run \\\n  -v \"$PWD:/usr/src/app\" \\\n  -w /usr/src/app \\\n  -p 8080:8080 \\\n  -it openjdk:8-alpine sh\n\ndocker pull maven:3.6-jdk-8-alpine\ndocker run \\\n  -v \"$PWD:/usr/src/app\" \\\n  -w /usr/src/app \\\n  -p 8080:8080 \\\n  -it maven:3.6-jdk-8-alpine sh"
